00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:28,600
[suyun altından sesler]

233
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:32,080
[öksürük sesi]

234
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:37,960
[su ve öksürük sesleri]

235
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,720
-[öksürük sesi]
-İyi misin?

236
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,760
Eyvallah. [hafif öksürük]

237
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:52,520
[su sesleri]

238
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:55,080
-[zorlanma nidası]
-[suya düşme sesi]

239
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,560
